@startuml Forgot-Password
actor Customer
participant "Frontend" as F
participant "Backend API" as B
database "Supabase" as DB

== Step 1: Request Reset ==
Customer -> F: Enter email on Forgot Password
F -> B: POST /auth/customer/forgot-password
B -> DB: Find customer by email
B -> DB: Create PasswordResetToken (1hr expiry)
B --> F: 200 + token
F --> Customer: Redirect to Reset Password

== Step 2: Reset with New Password ==
Customer -> F: Enter token, new password
F -> B: POST /auth/customer/reset-password
B -> DB: Validate token
B -> B: Hash new password
B -> DB: Update customer passwordHash
B -> DB: Mark token used
B --> F: 200 Success
F --> Customer: Redirect to Login
@enduml
